body:
### Welcome to Siva Tech.
Siva Tech is a tech company created by young software developers working with various companies in different domain and on their free time, they do community projects in e-commerce, trading and education.

All their products are available at Github for free download.

We welcome any pull request if there is a room to improve any functionalities

For any assistance contact info@siva-tech.com
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
